Author: AndiHon
Title: [ANN] DYLYVER ICO [DYCOIN Token] Ride sharing and social delivery service
Body: Dylyver is a sensational project - an ecosystem that helps in everyday life, and especially in sending and receiving courier parcels at low prices. The project has several platforms that are highly competitive:  1) The "Dylyver Drive" platform, which connects drivers and passengers, seems to be a place to store various data - senders, recipients of parcels and couriers. From here you can quickly enter information, also using the Android and IPhone applications.  2) A peer-to-peer platform for delivering "Dylyver Cargo" parcels, which combines courier and receiver senders.  3) A Dylyver Drive platform for sharing a ride that allows users to quickly order a vehicle at any time with just one click. A very convenient and quick solution. Dylyver Drive is an application for journeys on iPhone and Android devices. The user can become a driver within three days using a mobile phone and vehicle, registering as a partner in the Dylyver model.  You can pay for courier services by credit card, cash or cryptocurrency wallet. WOW !!!! It's exciting. The important thing is that you can track the route of shipments using a mobile application on Android or IPhone.  A big plus is that everyone on the Dylyver platform can be a sender, courier or recipient. Any interested, i.e. sender and recipient can track the location of your courier on the map and communicate with the courier via the chat function. WOW - it's just easier.  4) Via Dylyver platform that will allow you to send parcels to your relatives and friends quickly and at a reasonable price by people traveling in the same direction and having enough free space in the vehicle.   This is a fascinating project!

Author: galkinig
Title: [ANN] DYLYVER ICO [DYCOIN Token] Ride sharing and social delivery service
Body: New player in the ridesharing and package delivery markets   Dylyver is a ride sharing and on demand package delivery platform that aims to disrupt the transportation market by exploiting the benefits of blockchain technology and by introducing Dycoin token as a payment unit within its decentralized ecosystem. Together, our two proprietary mobile applications form one unique service and income system for users:   - A ridesharing solution that enables users to order a vehicle in a matter of seconds. - A package delivery platform where users can ship their packages with people that are travelling in the same direction.  By owning Dycoin tokens you get an opportunity to pay for taxi and package deliveries with the help of Dylyver applications, exchange Dycoin tokens to other cryptocurrencies and fiat money and pay for goods and services outside Dylyver ecosystem with Dylyver branded debit card.  - Dycoin tokens will be listed on the following exchanges Latoken, Bancor and Metamorph. More major ones to come. You can already purchase Dycoin tokens from Latoken exchange at https://wallet.latoken.com/market/ICO/ETH/DYC-ETH.  - Participate in our Airdrop. Double (2x) your airdrops tokens by purchasing Dycoin tokens for $30 on our web page. Link to the Airdrop: https://ico.dylyver.com/airdrop  - Participate in our referral program and earn additional Dycoin tokens from every single Dycoin purchase in your network. https://ico.dylyver.com  - You will soon be able to download and test our ride sharing application. (iOS & Android)

Title: [ANN] DYLYVER ICO [DYCOIN Token] Ride sharing and social delivery service
Body: Our mission is based on two mobile applications: the ride sharing platform "Dylyver Drive" that connects drivers and passengers, and a peer-to-peer platform for parcel delivery "Dylyver Cargo" that connects senders, couriers and receivers. Dylyver Drive is a ride sharing platform that allows users to quickly order a vehicle at any time whenever they are just with a click of a button. Dylyver Cargo is a social courier delivery service for parcels. Via Dylyver App users can now send parcels to their relatives and friends quickly and at a favourable price by people who travel in the same direction, and who have enough free space in the vehicle or in the backpack. Development of smart contracts and integration of ride sharing and package delivery platforms with Blockchain will allow the company to make a decentralized environment, where payments will be immediately and securely moved from user’s crypto wallet to driver’s or courier’s wallet upon successful trip or package delivery.

Development of smart contracts and integration of ride sharing and package delivery platforms with Blockchain will allow the company to make a decentralized environment, where payments will be immediately and securely moved from user’s crypto wallet to driver’s or courier’s wallet upon successful trip or package delivery.

Author: galkinig
Title: [ANN] DYLYVER ICO [DYCOIN Token] Ride sharing and social delivery service
Body: Ride sharing service and social transportation of blockchain era     https://i.imgur.com/nhMZC2w.jpg     https://dabuttonfactory.com/button.png?t=ICO+SITE&f=Calibri-Bold&ts=29&tc=fff&hp=20&vp=8&c=5&bgt=unicolored&bgc=e22b49&ebgc=e22b49     https://dabuttonfactory.com/button.png?t=Whitepaper&f=Calibri-Bold&ts=29&tc=fff&hp=20&vp=8&c=5&bgt=unicolored&bgc=32327b&ebgc=e22b49   What is Dylyver?  Dylyver is a technology corporation that created a ride sharing platform and social delivery marketplace.  The foundation of our business model is a decentralized, fully automated two-sided market for drivers and riders on one hand; and package senders, couriers, and recipients on the other. With the help of its two mobile apps (Driver and Cargo) Dylyver empowers its Users to order a vehicle in seconds and send valuable packages with people that are travelling in the same direction.   Problems we are solving  Integrating our ride sharing and package delivery platforms with Blockchain will allow us to make a decentralized system, where payments will be immediately and securely transferred from users crypto wallets to drivers/couriers wallets upon every successful trip/delivery. This way we are eliminating the high level of dependency on 3rd party payment systems and their high rates. Utilizing the benefits of Blockchain and smart contracts will also enable Dylyver to create a more secure package delivery system, where all the delivered packaged will be insured against theft and damage. Author: galkinig
Title: [ANN] DYLYVER ICO [DYCOIN Token] Ride sharing and social delivery service
Body: Dylyver partnership with Bancor cryptoexchange   https://i.imgur.com/zLqZMNc.jpg   Dylyver to integrate Bancor Protocol   Today marks a huge and exciting milestone for our team and all Dycoin holders!!!! We have partnered with Switzerland based Bancor, a decentralized liquidity network, to provide continuous liquidity for our tokens and empower Dycoin holders to convert their Dycoins to other cryptocurrencies.  By integrating the Bancor Protocol, Dycoin token holders will gain access to continuous liquidity regardless of trade volume or exchange listings, through the Bancor Network, where any integrated token can be automatically converted to any other directly from the Bancor Wallet or any Web3 wallet, such as MetaMask. Currently integrated tokens include ETH, BNT (the Bancor Network Token), GNO (Gnosis), BNB (Binance) and a long list of announced projects soon to be activated.  Dylyver will activate a Relay Token with 0.5% of its circulating token supply within the week following the successful completion of the Token Sale.   About Bancor  The Bancor Protocol is a standard for the creation of Smart Tokens™, cryptocurrencies with built-in convertibility directly through their smart contracts. Bancor utilizes an innovative token “connector” method to enable formulaic price calculation and continuous liquidity for all integrated tokens, without needing to match two parties in an exchange. Smart Tokens interconnect to form token liquidity networks, allowing user-generated cryptocurrencies to thrive. To convert tokens instantly, visit the Bancor Web App or join the Bancor Telegram group for more information.
